{#- ### Verdict — renders opening sentence, red HTML blockquote with worst-case bullets, closing sentence. -#}
{#- Inputs:  data.severity, data.opening, data.bullets[{title,body,refs}], data.closing, severity_emoji (filter-injected). -#}
